H3.text: What type of exhibit can be seen in the military museum at Bovington in Dorset. Tank

A4.text: The Tank Museum (previously the Bovington Tank Museum) is a collection of armoured fighting vehicles at Bovington Camp in Dorset

A5.text: It includes Tiger 131, the only working example of a German Tiger I tank
